text:
East River, shoreline, north from East 92nd to 96th Streets, showing the Riverside Fuel Co. coal yard between East 93rd and 94th Streets and the Consolidated Edison Co. plant between East 95th and 96th Streets.

October 1, 1934.

P. L. Sperr.
title: East River - Shore and skyline of Manhattan between East 92nd and 96th Streets - Queensborough Bridge.
